min vaible project:

Data:

	ProjectType: [Img, 2d, 3d, VR]
	Text: string
	
	Project: {
		Name: string
		Type: ProjectType
		projectUrl: urlString
		Created: date
		Updated: date
		NoteTexts: Text[]
	}
	
	Admin: {
		Username: string
		Password: Hash
		SessionId: Hash
	}
	
	Site: {
		SiteUpdated: date
		Projects: Project[]
	}





Home:

	Gallery
	-----------------
	Projects
	- Proj Name 1, last update
	- [name], [update date]
	- ...


Project:

	Project Name
	--------------
	
	|  Navigation             |
	| [Go back] [go to notes] |
	 -------------------------
	
	Demo
	[thumbnamil]
	
	{ if type <> 2d: // if img/2D, show full screen?
		[Play Project btn] { 
			if type = VR: go to ./view
			else: start video/canvas
		}
	}
	
	
	Notes
	------
	Created On: [date]
	Last updated on: [date]
	
	{...Notes text...}
	
	[Go to top]



New Project:
	Checks for Auth

	New Project
	--------------
	[Name]
	[type |v]
	thumbnail [upload pic]
	content {variable depending on type}
	Notes
	[NoteText]



























